  intruction: 'Warning: Gas Leak Hazard<br>A gas-related risk may be present in this
    area.<br>Look carefully and identify the source of the danger by clicking on
    it.'
  question: What is the safest action to take in case of a gas leak?
  answers:
  - Use electrical equipment near the leak
  - Ventilate the area and stop the gas leak if possible
  - Stay close to monitor the leak
  correctIndex: 1
  securedText: Risk secured.<br>The gas leak has been safely managed.<br>Well done.
